      <title>Abrdn 建议在预算前就英国印花税做出妥协</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-17/abrdn-suggests-compromise-on-uk-stamp-duty-ahead-of-budget</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Abrdn Plc 在英国印花税辩论中采取了中间立场，主张取消对非蓝筹股的印花税，因为在财政大臣 Rachel Reeves 出台首份预算之前，要求全面废除印花税的呼声已经消退。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-17/abrdn-suggests-compromise-on-uk-stamp-duty-ahead-of-budget</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 17 Oct 2024 11:53:57 GMT</pubDate>
